{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_BishopAttack2}}
'''A_BishopAttack2'''

(no parameters)

Fires a single {{Class|BishopFX}} projectile.  Decrements the counter set by [[A_BishopAttack]].  If the counter reaches 0 or the target is lost then it will jump back to the See state.

This code pointer is restricted to {{Class|Bishop}} and actors inheriting from it.

